==English==
===Expression===
'''[[no]] [[smoke|smoking]]'''

# A phrase used in notices indicating that the [[smoke|smoking]] of [[cigarette]]s, etc., is not permitted in the surrounding area. May be used together with a [http://forum.cptec.org/index.php?showtopic=334 prohibition sign].

